{"tid":1389264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大巴拿換盧卡古 已達成協議","createTime":"2019-07-31T00:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:28:14.000Z","uid":122620,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3045f013b4c141786f430d2b418255029b29ff95","tid":1389264,"uid":122620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/31/085335_96fefd186d8d874392e3a8eda514ef8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F31%2F085335_96fefd186d8d874392e3a8eda514ef8c.png&h=c72c1f45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d1df35edc52c6f6eaf0b2c7a472a0994ad31d92","tid":1389264,"uid":5190,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:55:19.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d3263428ad04705c71623872ff4441ef5e0e170a","tid":1389264,"uid":122620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:28:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"}]}